<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
  <head>
    <meta content='text/html; charset=UTF-8' http-equiv='Content-Type' />
    <style>
      body {
        font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
        line-height: 1.6;
        color: #333;
      }
      .header {
        background-color: #4CAF50;
        color: white;
        padding: 20px;
        text-align: center;
      }
      .content {
        padding: 20px;
      }
      .logo {
        max-width: 200px;
        height: auto;
      }
      .footer {
        background-color: #f1f1f1;
        padding: 10px;
        text-align: center;
        font-size: 12px;
        color: #666;
      }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <div class="header">
      <% if attachments['logo.png'].present? %>
        <%= image_tag attachments['logo.png'].url, alt: 'Logo', class: 'logo' %>
      <% end %>
      <h1>Your Monthly Report</h1>
    </div>

    <div class="content">
      <p>Dear <%= @target.respond_to?(:name) ? @target.name : 'User' %>,</p>

      <p>
        Your monthly activity report for <%= Date.current.last_month.strftime('%B %Y') %> is ready!
      </p>

      <p>
        This report contains detailed information about your activity and notifications
        during the past month. Please find your monthly report attached to this email.
      </p>

      <h2>Quick Summary</h2>
      <% if @target.respond_to?(:notifications) %>
        <ul>
          <li>Total notifications: <%= @target.notifications.count %></li>
          <li>Opened: <%= @target.notifications.opened_only.count rescue 0 %></li>
          <li>Unopened: <%= @target.notifications.unopened_only.count rescue 0 %></li>
        </ul>
      <% end %>

      <p>
        The attached PDF contains a comprehensive breakdown of your activity.
        Additionally, we've included a CSV file with the raw data for your records.
      </p>

      <p>
        If you have any questions about this report, please don't hesitate to contact us.
      </p>

      <p>
        Best regards,<br/>
        The Activity Notification Team
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="footer">
      <p>
        This is an automated email from Activity Notification.
        Please do not reply to this email.
      </p>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
